{
  "chapter": 7,
  "chapter_summary": "燕十三在马车中与薛可人交谈，薛可人透露自己是第七次从丈夫夏侯星身边出逃，希望利用燕十三让夏侯星误以为她已是他的人。马车突然被截停，夏侯星赶来追妻。燕十三被迫与夏侯星交手，首次使出三少爷那一剑，威力远超预期，一招便将夏侯星击飞。夏侯星不甘，再次挑战，竟想出了三少爷那一剑的破法，但燕十三的剑势在破绽处自行变化，千蛇剑被击断。燕十三由此领悟三少爷那一剑根本无破绽可寻，心中大震。一个神秘流浪汉突然出现，识破了老车夫的真实身份——夏侯飞山，红云谷二十年前失踪的最强高手。燕十三揭穿老车夫身份，章节在悬念中结束。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我有毒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "好像没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "大概也没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你怕什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "我只不过想知道一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "我只想知道你究竟想要我干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你以为我这么样对你，只因为我想要你做件事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实这并不是我第一次溜走，我已经溜过七次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你猜我被抓回去几次？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "七次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "夏侯星这个人别的本事没有，只有一样最大的本事！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "不管我溜到哪里，他都有本事把我抓回去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "这本事倒真不小。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "所以这次他迟早一定还是会找到我的。幸好这次已不同了！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "有什么不同？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "这次他抓住我的时候，我已经是你的人。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "至少他总会认为我已经是你的人！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "他这人还有另外一种本事，他很会吃醋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "所以他看见我们这样子，一定会杀了你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "如果别人要杀你，而且非要杀你不可，你怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你当然也只有杀了他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "可是你也用不着叹气，因为你并没有吃亏，有很多男人都愿意为了我这样的女孩子杀人的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "我相信一定有很多男人会，可是我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你也一样！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "你怎么知道我也一样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "因为到了那时候，你根本就没有选择的余地。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "到了那时候，你不杀他，他也要杀你，所以你现在还不如……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你看他是不是真的有本事？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "speaker_name": "夏侯星",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贱人，滚出来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "speaker_name": "夏侯星",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "不许出来。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "text": "你知道我是一向最听你话的，可是现在你又叫我滚出去，又不许我出去，我怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "看样子他是要你滚出去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "绝不是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "因为我既不是贱人，也不会滚。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "text": "我知道夏侯公子一向是个有教养的人，如果他要我出去，一定会客客气气的说个请字。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "speaker_name": "夏侯星",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "请，请，请，请……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "text": "你究竟要请我干什么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "speaker_name": "夏侯星",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我要请你去死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到你的剑法比我想像中还要高得多。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也想不到。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "text": "你还想干什么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "speaker_name": "夏侯星",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "请。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "text": "还想请我去死？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "speaker_name": "夏侯星",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "阁下刚才用的那一剑，的确是天下无双的剑法！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "speaker_name": "夏侯星",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "在下此来，就是还想领教领教阁下刚才那一剑。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "text": "你还想再接那一剑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "speaker_name": "夏侯星",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "text": "请。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_lang_han",
      "speaker_name": "流浪汉",
      "listener": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老车夫",
      "listener": "char_liu_lang_han",
      "text": "好？好什么？什么好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_lang_han",
      "speaker_name": "流浪汉",
      "listener": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "text": "你好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老车夫",
      "listener": "char_liu_lang_han",
      "text": "我什么地方好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_lang_han",
      "speaker_name": "流浪汉",
      "listener": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "text": "你什么地方都好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_lang_han",
      "speaker_name": "流浪汉",
      "listener": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "text": "刚才若是你自己去，现在那个人已死了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪奇怪，这个人我怎么看起来很面熟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老车夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪奇怪，这个人究竟在说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "text": "他说的话别人也许不懂，可是我懂。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老车夫",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "text": "不但我懂，你也懂。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "text": "二十年前，红云谷最强的高手，并不是现在的庄主夏侯重山。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老车夫",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "不是老庄主是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "text": "是他的弟弟夏侯飞山。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老车夫",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "可是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "text": "可是夏侯飞山在二十年前就已忽然失踪，至今没有人知道他的下落。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老车夫",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "只怕他老人家早已死了很久了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 391,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "text": "江湖中人都以为他已死了，现在我才知道他并没有死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老车夫",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你怎么知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "text": "因为我已知道他的下落。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老车夫",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "他老人家在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 399,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "text": "就在这里！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "text": "夏侯飞山就是你！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_lao_che_fu",
      "text": "远在二十年前，你就已会过夺命十三剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 411,
      "line_end": 411
    }
